    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Me</h1>

    <p class="text-lg mb-6">
      I'm a software engineer based near Paris. I've been writing code professionally
      since around 2011 — mostly backend work, PHP and Symfony for a long time,
      TypeScript and Python more recently.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-6">
      I'm currently founding engineer at{" "}
      <a href="https://sluicebox.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Sluicebox.ai</a>,
      where I build the product and platform end-to-end. Small team, manufacturing industry,
      lots of LLMs and PostgreSQL and figuring out what actually matters to customers.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Interests</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>
        <strong>Home automation</strong> — Home Assistant, Zigbee, ESPHome.
